{"tid":1633814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三權分立","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T15:08:24.000Z","uid":24465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1bc8d2b6413b0dc7cb87fe87003897021cf0467","tid":1633814,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"以往香港嘅三權分立：<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.matters.news/embed/14bf6414-b4b8-4272-8238-30a5abf7dabe/h-klesson1-021.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.matters.news%2Fembed%2F14bf6414-b4b8-4272-8238-30a5abf7dabe%2Fh-klesson1-021.png&h=6fdd9c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現今香港嘅三權分立：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKaMRzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKaMRzQ.jpg&h=3ff88212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有感而發鳩整下圖<br />\n拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"f66e45b287522f255e59d8efb2e61f9e73e5802b","tid":1633814,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:20:30.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"edf07f73696590b60f1050ef8e7903abb20fdb17","tid":1633814,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"所謂「和理非」回合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633715</a>"},{"pid":"ec0ae295b9af4e9ca366e072edd2dc4fb437d44f","tid":1633814,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc366b8ad53e5b28222a7874278a852def07769","tid":1633814,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab1567038afa9ec401a5b9c9a1ef2619bf1199e","tid":1633814,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}